    "name": "ETH-Liq-LTV-TPP-COM-COL-BUF-1mon-30-100Y1Y-daily",
    "description": "ACTUS DeFi ETH Portfolio: 100-YEAR PERPETUAL MODEL with 1-YEAR SIMULATION\n\n═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\nKEY CHANGES FROM 30-DAY VERSION:\n  ✅ Maturity Date: 2126-02-18 (100 years from IED)\n  ✅ Simulation Period: 1 year (2026-02-18 to 2027-02-18)\n  ✅ Age Dimension: Stays <1% throughout year (vs 100% in 30 days)\n  ✅ True DeFi Perpetual Semantics (no MD event generated)\n═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════\n\nPORTFOLIO STRUCTURE:\n═══════════════════════════════════════════════════\nTotal ETH: 7.0 ETH\n  - Collateral ETH: 3.0 ETH (pledged to loan)\n  - Buffer ETH: 4.0 ETH (uncommitted reserve)\n\nContracts:\n1. COM (ETH-Collateral-CompetingRisk-01): 3.0 ETH collateral\n2. COM (ETH-Buffer-Portfolio-01): 4.0 ETH buffer\n3. PAM (DeFi-ETH-CompetingRisk-01): $5,000 loan with behavioral models\n\nTRACKING CAPABILITIES:\n- Total ETH value over time (7.0 ETH × ETH_USD price)\n- Collateral value tracking (3.0 ETH × price)\n- Buffer value tracking (4.0 ETH × price)\n- LTV based on collateral only (3.0 ETH)\n- True portfolio LTV (using all 7.0 ETH)\n\nBEHAVIORAL MODELS:\n  1. TwoDimensionalPrepaymentModel — voluntary rate-driven deleveraging\n  2. CollateralLTVModel — protocol-enforced LTV (uses 3.0 ETH only)\n\nScenario: Same as original for first 30 days (ETH: $2,800 → $1,870, Rate: 5.0% → 7.65%)\n         Then constant extrapolation for days 31-365\n\nNOTE: You'll need to extend rate and price indices to 365 days for full 1-year data.\n      Current indices have 30 days; simulation will extrapolate last values.\n\nOpen Postman Console (Ctrl+Alt+C) before running.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
